view: -t
compress: -c
extract: -x
verboze: -v
file: -f (must be last)

Tar with compress
tar -c -x: -cvf -xvf .tar
gzip -z: -cvzf -xvzf .tar.gz
bzip2 -j -y: -cvjf -xvjf .tar.bz2 (smaller)
xz -c -d: xz -9 -c - > file.tar.xz, xz -d file.tar.xz (smallest)

No tar
zip: file.zip directory


Combo instructions:
https://github.com/jrcharney/rigel/wiki/Download-using-curl-and-tar
